<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٨٦٢ - حَدِيثٌ <span class="c2">(حم)</span> : <span class="c1">" لا نُورَثُ مَا تَرَكْنَا صَدَقَةٌ "</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">فِي تَرْجَمَةِ:</span> مَالِكِ بْنِ أَوْسِ بْنِ الْحَدَثَانِ، عَنْ عُمَرَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>